; SN76489 PSG — three independent tone channels
; No FM instrument definitions needed for PSG parts

; Set tempo for all channels
'B1 T120
'B2 T120
'B3 T120

; Channel B1 — melody (pentatonic scale)
'B1 v100 l8 o4 c d e g a g e d c2

; Channel B2 — counter-melody (offset by one beat)
'B2 v80 l8 o3 r2 g a >c d< a g e d2

; Channel B3 — bass pedal
'B3 v70 l2 o2 c g c g
